## ‚öôÔ∏è Setup Instructions

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Create Trello API Key and Token
- Go to: [https://trello.com/app-key](https://trello.com/app-key)
- Copy your **Key**
- Click **‚ÄúToken‚Äù** to generate your personal access token  
> ‚ö†Ô∏è Keep these secure ‚Äì they grant access to your Trello account.

---

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Create Postman Environment
Add the following variables in your environment:

| Variable | Example Value |
|-----------|----------------|
| `baseURL` | `https://api.trello.com` |
| `key` | `your_trello_key_here` |
| `token` | `your_trello_token_here` |

---
### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Import the Collection
1. Open Postman  
2. Click **Import ‚Üí File**  
3. Select the file: `Trello_Full_Automation.postman_collection.json`  
4. Select your environment (`TrelloEnv`)  
5. Click **Run Collection**
